exports[`changelog > changelog 5.21.0 --format markdown 1`] = `
"## 5.21.0 (2024-09-22)

  💄 Button - 💄 Button adds \`textColor\`, \`textHoverColor\` and \` textActiveColor\` tokens. [](https://github.com/madocto)
  🆕 FloatButton - 🆕 FloatButton supports \`placement\` property, allowing menus to pop up from multiple directions. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🆕 FloatButton - 🆕 FloatButton supports \`htmlType\` prop. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  💄 FloatButton - 💄 Unify FloatButton and FloatButton.Group button round style. [](https://github.com/Layouwen)
  💄 FloatButton - 💄 Manage FloatButton's \`z-index\` with \`useZIndex\` to improve compatibility with other popup components. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🆕 Menu - 🆕 Menu.Item and Dropdown's \`menu\` supports \`extra\` prop now. [-ice](https://github.com/coding-ice)
  🐞 Menu - 🐞 Fix Menu \`popupStyle\` not working on SubMenu. [](https://github.com/Wxh16144)
  🆕 Table - 🆕 Table supports \`minWidth\` for columns. [](https://github.com/linxianxi)
  🐞 Table - 🐞 Fix Table empty and shadow issues in virtual mode. [](https://github.com/linxianxi)
  🐞 Table - 🐞 Fix Table column selection issue where deselection was not possible under certain circumstances. [](https://github.com/Jarryxin)
  🆕 Input - 🆕 Input.OTP support \`type\` to help handle some case need number only. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 Input - 🐞 Fix Select inside Input addon text color when Select is focused. [](https://github.com/DDDDD12138)
  🛠 Modal - ⌨️ Fix Modal throws warning \`avoid using aria-hidden on a focused element or its ancestor\`. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🆕 Modal - 🆕 Modal supports \`closable.disabled\` prop now. [](https://github.com/Ke1sy)
  🐞 Descriptions - 🐞 Fix Descriptions column is missing in some cases. [](https://github.com/yezhonghu0503)
  🐞 Descriptions - 🐞 Revert to fix the issue where the popup layer component inside Descriptions is being cut off. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🆕 Upload - 🆕 Upload will pass \`name\` prop to \`<input type="file" />\`. [](https://github.com/Wxh16144)
  🆕 Upload - 🆕 Upload \`showUploadList.showXxxIcon\` accept a function value now. [](https://github.com/guoyunhe)
  🐞 ColorPicker - 🐞 Fix ColorPicker when type hex input may not get correct color with precision issue. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 ColorPicker - 🐞 Adjust ColorPicker popup panel not lock by \`value\` to allow control mode with \`onChangeComplete\` scenarios. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 App - 🐞 Fixed App warn about \`zIndex\` too large when using the \`modal\` with having popup component method via \`useApp\`. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 App - 🐞 Fix App rtl style does not respect ConfigProvider direction prop. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🆕 Pagination - 🆕 Pagination \`showSizeChanger\` accepts Select props now. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  💄 Pagination - 💄 Remove Pagination default font family. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  💄 Select - 💄 Add more tokens for Select to customize hover/focus style. [-tang](https://github.com/kiner-tang)
  🐞 Select - 🐞 Fix Select search text overlap with arrow icon. [](https://github.com/yezhonghu0503)
  🐞 Select - 🐞 Fix Select extra background of clear icon when enable \`allowClear\` and \`variant="filled"\`. [](https://github.com/thinkasany)
  🆕 Select 🆕 Segmented adds \`vertical\` property and improves accessibility. [](https://github.com/liangchaofei)
  🆕 Select 🆕 Radio.Group supports \`block\` prop now. [](https://github.com/yuanliu147)
  🆕 Select 🆕 ConfigProvider supports configuring the \`className\` and \`style\` properties of the Splitter component. [-jia-nan](https://github.com/li-jia-nan)
  🆕 Select 🆕 Image add \`onActive\` to \`toolbarRender\` for toggling images . [](https://github.com/madocto)
  🆕 Select 🆕 Add ref on List component. [](https://github.com/Asanio06)
  🆕 Select 🆕 Collapse support \`classNames\` and \`styles\` for semantic style customization. [](https://github.com/wanpan11)
  💄 Select 💄 Make Skeleton.Node custom node by remove it's default icon children. [](https://github.com/afc163)
  🐞 Select 🐞 Fix Layout.Sider can not modify theme when used alone. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 Select 🐞 Fix Typography \`copyable\` with array \`children\` has additional \`,\` string issue. [](https://github.com/zombieJ)
  🐞 Select 🐞 Fix Tour where long title will overlap with close button. [-tang](https://github.com/kiner-tang)
  🛠 Select 🌐 Localization
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Checkbox adds onFocus\` and \`onBlur\` in type definition. [](https://github.com/huiliangShen)
  🛠 TypeScript - 🤖 Fix Badge property type definition to support passing mouse events. [](https://github.com/yuanliu147)"
`;

